    <preface>
      <p><i>This draft Code of Practice is laid before Parliament under sections 43(7), 52(8) and 60(7) of the Digital Economy Act 2017 for approval by resolution of each House. </i></p>
      <p><i>Responsibility for functions under section 43 is proposed to be transferred from the Minister for the Cabinet Office to the Secretary of State using the Ministers of the Crown Act 1975 before this Code is issued. If that transfer has not taken effect when the Code is issued, the Code will instead be issued in relation to Public Service Delivery by the Minister for the Cabinet Office.</i></p>
    </preface>
